long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
J-Queue is a Chrome extension that adds queue functionality for j-novel.club, the website to read official licensed light novel content. Using this Chrome Extension, a user selects which Light Novels Series to follow. The extension will display the unread chapters for each of the selected series. The extension automatically updates its list as the user reads chapters or as new chapters are released.
